{"id":"cubic-equation","slug":"cubic-equation-calculator","name":"Cubic Equation Calculator","category":"algebra","icon":"x³","description":"Analyze cubic equations ax³ + bx² + cx + d = 0. Calculate discriminant and evaluate at specific x values.","tags":["cubic equation","roots","algebra","polynomial"],"fields":[{"id":"a","label":"a (x³ coefficient)","type":"number","defaultValue":1,"constraint":{"step":0.01}},{"id":"b","label":"b (x² coefficient)","type":"number","defaultValue":-6},{"id":"c","label":"c (x coefficient)","type":"number","defaultValue":11},{"id":"d","label":"d (constant)","type":"number","defaultValue":-6},{"id":"xTest","label":"Test x value","type":"number","defaultValue":1},{"id":"fAtX","label":"f(x) at test value","type":"computed","precision":6,"helpText":"Substitute x into the cubic"},{"id":"discriminant","label":"Simplified discriminant part","type":"computed","precision":4},{"id":"sumRoots","label":"Sum of roots (-b/a)","type":"computed","precision":4},{"id":"productRoots","label":"Product of roots (-d/a)","type":"computed","precision":4}],"groups":[{"id":"inputs","label":"Coefficients","fields":["a","b","c","d","xTest"]},{"id":"outputs","label":"Analysis","fields":["fAtX","sumRoots","productRoots","discriminant"]}],"formulas":{"fAtX":"a*xTest^3 + b*xTest^2 + c*xTest + d","sumRoots":"-b/a","productRoots":"-d/a","discriminant":"18*a*b*c*d - 4*b^3*d + b^2*c^2 - 4*a*c^3 - 27*a^2*d^2"},"explanation":"## Cubic Equation\n\nFor **ax³ + bx² + cx + d = 0**:\n\n- **Sum of roots** = −b/a\n- **Sum of products of pairs** = c/a\n- **Product of roots** = −d/a\n- **Discriminant Δ > 0**: 3 real roots\n- **Δ = 0**: repeated root\n- **Δ < 0**: 1 real + 2 complex roots","examples":[{"label":"x³ - 6x² + 11x - 6 = 0 (roots: 1,2,3)","inputs":{"a":1,"b":-6,"c":11,"d":-6,"xTest":1}},{"label":"x³ - 3x + 2 = 0","inputs":{"a":1,"b":0,"c":-3,"d":2,"xTest":1}}]}
